HEADWORD: Showery
<hw>Show"er*y</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Raining
in showers; abounding with frequent showers of rain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Of or pertaining to a shower or showers.</def>
